data.description:
Welcome to your new Home, this beautiful well taken care of home features   4 bed 3 bath with a loft  for extra space, entertainment or even an office , garage was converted  to a beautiful large Bedroom. Located  on a very desirable area near i-10 & shopping centers.
As you step outside, you'll find a backyard eagerly awaiting your personal touch to finish it into your own special outdoor oasis for relaxation and entertainment. Whether you envision a cozy patio, a vibrant garden, or a serene retreat, the possibilities are endless. Overall, this home provides the ideal setting for a spacious and comfortable lifestyle, offering multiple rooms and amenities that cater to the needs of a large family and their entertaining endeavors.
